<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your OTP Code</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333333;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666666;
        }

        .otp-code {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333333;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #eeeeee;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #999999;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Your OTP Code</h1>
        <p>Use the following OTP code to complete your registration:</p>
        <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
        <p>This code will expire in 20 minutes. If you did not request this code, please ignore this email.</p>
        <p class="footer">Thank you for choosing our service.</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>